title: India and China seek to re-set a rocky relationship
text:
India and China seek to re-set a rocky relationship 42
Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi met with Chinese President Xi Jinping on Friday, on the first day of an ice-breaking visit to China in which the giant neighbors will seek to re-set a troubled relationship.
